description:
Various data sets showing ocean circulations/systems in the Barents sea.

Source Map Name: ETOPO5/paper maps
Projection: geographic
Projection_meas: decimal degrees
Feature_type: polyarcpt
Vector 

ArcInfo coverage of the bathymetry of the Barents Sea in geographic
coordinates. The coverage was converted from a raster image (ETOPO5)
and digitising of paper maps. The coverage has a 'jagged' appearance.
